{"comments":"Texture Types — ADTs for texture mode, pattern, and coordinate mapping.\n\n## Design Philosophy\n\nTexture adds surface character to brush strokes, simulating the feel of\npainting on canvas, paper, or other materials. Unlike dual brush (which\ncombines two brush tips), texture applies a continuous pattern that affects\nhow paint deposits on the surface.\n\n## Texture Mode\n\nHow texture values affect the paint:\n\n- **Multiply**: Darkens paint where texture is dark (most common)\n- **Subtract**: Cuts into paint, revealing canvas\n- **Height**: Simulates surface height affecting paint flow\n- **ColorBurn**: Intense darkening effect\n- **SoftLight**: Subtle variation without hard edges\n\n## Texture Pattern\n\nBuilt-in patterns for common surfaces:\n\n- **CanvasWeave**: Artist canvas texture\n- **PaperGrain**: Standard paper surface\n- **ColdPress**: Watercolor paper (rough)\n- **HotPress**: Smooth illustration board\n- **Linen/Denim**: Fabric weaves\n- **Concrete/WoodGrain/Leather**: Material surfaces\n- **Noise/Clouds**: Procedural patterns\n- **Crosshatch**: Line-based pattern\n\n## Texture Coordinates\n\nHow the texture maps to the canvas:\n\n- **Tile**: Repeats infinitely (default)\n- **Stretch**: Fits to canvas size\n- **Center**: Single centered texture\n- **Mirror**: Mirrors at edges\n\n## Depth Control\n\nWhat input controls texture intensity:\n\n- **Off**: Constant depth\n- **Pressure**: Pen pressure varies depth\n- **Tilt**: Pen angle varies depth\n- **Velocity**: Stroke speed varies depth\n- **Random**: Per-dab random depth\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- Prelude\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[151,20],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Brush/Texture/Types.purs","start":[151,3]},"title":"TextureMultiply"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[152,20],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Brush/Texture/Types.purs","start":[152,3]},"title":"TextureSubtract"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[153,18],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Brush/Texture/Types.purs","start":[153,3]},"title":"TextureHeight"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[154,21],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Brush/Texture/Types.purs","start":[154,3]},"title":"TextureColorBurn"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[155,21],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Brush/Texture/Types.purs","start":[155,3]},"title":"TextureSoftLight"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Brush","Texture","Types"],"TextureMode"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[157,48],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Brush/Texture/Types.purs","start":[157,1]},"title":"eqTextureMode"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Ord"],"Ord"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Brush","Texture","Types"],"TextureMode"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[158,50],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Brush/Texture/Types.purs","start":[158,1]},"title":"ordTextureMode"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Brush","Texture","Types"],"TextureMode"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[165,52],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Brush/Text